55
00:04:03,270 --> 00:04:05,670
It’s OK

56
00:04:05,670 --> 00:04:06,630
even if you can’t see.

57
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:09,270
The wedding will be held as scheduled.

58
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:10,630
Don’t worry.

59
00:04:12,830 --> 00:04:15,030
I’ll go home and make you some soup.

60
00:04:15,110 --> 00:04:16,720
Junhao will be here with you.

61
00:04:44,510 --> 00:04:45,320
Junhao,

62
00:04:47,270 --> 00:04:49,350
can you give me my bag?

63
00:05:10,950 --> 00:05:12,510
Tell me what you need. I’ll get it.

64
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:15,040
Open it.

65
00:05:27,830 --> 00:05:30,110
After you came back from Guanmei,

66
00:05:30,510 --> 00:05:32,510
I found it in your pocket.

67
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:34,790
I kept it

68
00:05:35,950 --> 00:05:37,600
because I wanted you to know

69
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:40,510
that I could forgive you

70
00:05:41,110 --> 00:05:42,880
despite this unexpected incident.

71
00:05:48,950 --> 00:05:49,830
Yunyi...

72
00:05:49,830 --> 00:05:51,480
Since we were little,

73
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,950
you’ve been my sun

74
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:56,950
and my hope.

75
00:05:57,830 --> 00:06:00,270
I tried so hard to be good enough for you

76
00:06:00,510 --> 00:06:02,950
and to be able to stand next to you

77
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:05,320
to show my best side

78
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:06,950
to you.

79
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,720
But...

80
00:06:13,550 --> 00:06:15,110
to you,

81
00:06:16,670 --> 00:06:18,550
all my effort seems to be meaningless.

82
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:27,790
You mistook a false encounter

83
