as fate.

84
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:32,600
That was on the spur of the moment.

85
00:06:33,950 --> 00:06:35,230
How long

86
00:06:35,230 --> 00:06:36,760
have you known Ye Qianyu?

87
00:06:37,320 --> 00:06:39,510
You’re only curious about her.

88
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,550
That’s not love.

89
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:46,640
Yunyi.

90
00:06:49,110 --> 00:06:51,550
I know how I feel about Ye Qianyu.

91
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,200
Junhao,

92
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:08,200
I won’t let you go.

93
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:13,040
You should also think again.

94
00:08:06,440 --> 00:08:07,350
Director Xu,

95
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,200
I’m surprised

96
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:11,640
that you asked to see me

97
00:08:12,950 --> 00:08:15,000
in the middle of nowhere.

98
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:18,880
I believe you have a good reason for it.

99
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:30,830
Hope you can be smarter this time

100
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:33,350
and don’t put your own head on the chopping block.

101
00:08:33,470 --> 00:08:34,670
Isn’t she that attendant

102
00:08:34,670 --> 00:08:35,640
in Senwell Hotel?

103
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,590
Yes,

104
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:39,320
