105
00:08:42,910 --> 00:08:45,150
So she’s that village girl I’ve heard rumors of!

106
00:08:46,470 --> 00:08:48,400
No wonder Shan Junhao beat me.

107
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:51,520
But...

108
00:08:52,910 --> 00:08:54,150
Why did you give me these?

109
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,640
This is her personal information.

110
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:02,670
Do I need to teach you how to write the story?

111
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,440
Of course not.

112
00:09:05,470 --> 00:09:07,000
