113
00:09:11,400 --> 00:09:12,790
It’s juicy.

114
00:09:13,470 --> 00:09:15,080
A huge bomb!

115
00:09:20,110 --> 00:09:21,150
I get it.

116
00:09:22,790 --> 00:09:23,910
You’re doing this

117
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:26,080
