122
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,080
Chief Xie.

123
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,230
I believe you won’t be so dumb

124
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:40,760
and write things you shouldn’t have in the story.

125
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,200
Of course not.

126
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:45,080
I have professional ethics.

127
00:09:46,790 --> 00:09:48,200
Looking forward to seeing your work

128
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,320
on the headline tomorrow.

129
00:09:51,150 --> 00:09:52,000
Glad doing business with you.

130
00:09:57,790 --> 00:09:59,080
