Ziqian,

165
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:19,790
wedding planning is complex.

166
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:21,760
Please help Junhao

167
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:23,150
with the preparation.

168
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:37,030
What’s wrong?

169
00:11:39,300 --> 00:11:41,820
= Senwell Shan Junhao’s Affair with Grocery Girl =

170
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:45,590
What happened?

171
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:01,710
I knew that girl

172
00:12:01,710 --> 00:12:03,470
