174
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,030
I’m heading back to Guanmei.

175
00:12:14,030 --> 00:12:15,350
Chen and Shengzhe are at home.

176
00:12:15,350 --> 00:12:16,350
You can’t go out.

177
00:12:16,650 --> 00:12:17,530
If you go,

178
00:12:17,530 --> 00:12:18,620
you’ll be hunted by all.

179
00:12:18,620 --> 00:12:20,220
