180
00:12:20,220 --> 00:12:22,080
Stay here. I’ll go see them.

181
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:24,030
But...

182
00:12:25,030 --> 00:12:26,710
Qianyu, trust me.

183
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:28,880
I can protect Mama Jinzhi and Shengzhe.

184
00:12:31,710 --> 00:12:32,790
I’ll be back soon.

185
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,760
Drive safe.

