204
00:13:22,280 --> 00:13:23,710
Don’t check your phone

205
00:13:23,880 --> 00:13:24,670
or go out.

206
00:13:25,550 --> 00:13:27,030
I’ll fix it.

207
00:13:33,640 --> 00:13:34,550
I don’t know anything!

