221
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:51,480
- Leave us alone! - Leave!

222
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:53,070
- Get out of here! - Get the hell out!

223
00:13:53,110 --> 00:13:54,030
Why are you helping her?

224
00:13:54,030 --> 00:13:55,150
What’s your relationship with Ye Qianyu?

225
00:13:55,230 --> 00:13:56,280
- Say something. - Explain it to us.

226
00:13:56,280 --> 00:13:57,200
Stop! Follow me.

227
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:58,200
Come with me!

228
00:13:59,260 --> 00:13:59,980
Leave us alone!

229
00:14:01,150 --> 00:14:02,590
- Stop following us! - Get in!

230
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:03,960
Let’s go!

231
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:04,570
Get in the car.

232
00:14:05,100 --> 00:14:06,860
- Step back! Move! - Let’s go.

233
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,030
Hurry up!

234
00:14:09,880 --> 00:14:11,720
- Don’t leave! - Come back!

235
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:14,710
