239
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:30,640
Yeah. How could this happen?

240
00:14:30,640 --> 00:14:32,350
We saw it on the news.

241
00:14:33,880 --> 00:14:34,760
Where’s Qianyu?

242
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,640
She’s with Taichu.

243
00:14:37,640 --> 00:14:38,670
Aunt Jinzhi,

244
00:14:38,710 --> 00:14:40,710
when boss saw reporters heading to your store,

245
00:14:40,710 --> 00:14:42,470
he left at once to save you.

246
00:14:46,880 --> 00:14:48,150
Oh, crap!

247
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:50,520
I forgot to lock the cash register!

248
00:14:51,760 --> 00:14:52,470
Don’t worry.

249
00:14:52,640 --> 00:14:53,350
I’ll go.

250
00:14:56,110 --> 00:14:56,960
Sheng,

251
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:58,960
arrange a room for Jinzhi to rest.

252
00:14:59,400 --> 00:15:00,150
Fengqiao,

253
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:01,640
you take Shengzhe to school.

254
00:15:01,760 --> 00:15:02,960
Don’t tell anyone

255
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:04,080
that Jinzhi is here.

256
00:15:04,230 --> 00:15:05,640
