262
00:15:29,420 --> 00:15:30,740
Who is this?

263
00:15:30,740 --> 00:15:32,490
- Do you know him? - Don’t know.

264
00:15:33,260 --> 00:15:34,940
- Who’s this? - No idea.

265
00:15:36,940 --> 00:15:37,550
Hello.

266
00:15:37,760 --> 00:15:39,350
Excuse me, do you know Ye Qianyu?

267
00:15:39,780 --> 00:15:40,910
Do you know her?

268
00:15:40,910 --> 00:15:41,960
Sorry, don’t know.

269
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:43,120
You know where Ye Qianyu is?

270
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:44,740
Yes. Tell us.

271
00:15:48,280 --> 00:15:49,400
You’re still here?

272
00:15:50,280 --> 00:15:51,960
I said I don’t know.

273
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:53,000
Even if I did,

274
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:54,150
I wouldn’t tell you.

275
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:55,640
Stop asking me.

276
00:15:55,640 --> 00:15:57,200
Excuse me. Sorry.

277
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:59,450
- Don’t leave. - Can you tell us anything?

278
00:16:02,640 --> 00:16:03,400
Tang.

279
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:04,440
Where’s Mama Jinzhi?

280
00:16:05,350 --> 00:16:06,320
In the inn.

281
00:16:07,470 --> 00:16:08,230
That’s a relief.

282
00:16:08,550 --> 00:16:09,320
Hey,

283
00:16:09,640 --> 00:16:10,880
isn’t Qianyu at your place?

284
00:16:10,880 --> 00:16:12,030
Why are you here?

285
00:16:13,590 --> 00:16:14,790
I’ll tell you later.

