00:16:14,790 --> 00:16:15,590
Let’s go back first.

287
00:16:15,590 --> 00:16:17,070
Sure. Let’s go.

288
00:16:19,550 --> 00:16:20,230
Say something.

289
00:16:21,470 --> 00:16:22,590
Stop asking us.

290
00:16:33,670 --> 00:16:35,670
The best way to clarify the rumor

291
00:16:35,880 --> 00:16:38,520
is to have Junhao and Yunyi marry now.

292
00:16:38,840 --> 00:16:40,760
Aunt Jiang, what?

293
00:16:41,640 --> 00:16:43,590
Once they get married,

294
00:16:43,590 --> 00:16:45,520
the rumor will disappear itself.

295
00:16:46,590 --> 00:16:48,200
But right now, Yunyi...

296
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:51,000
Nothing needs to be clarified.

297
00:16:52,880 --> 00:16:54,110
It isn’t the time

298
00:16:54,110 --> 00:16:55,710
to be stubborn now.

299
00:16:56,320 --> 00:16:57,080
Don’t you know

300
00:16:57,080 --> 00:16:58,790
how serious this matter is?

301
00:17:04,470 --> 00:17:05,190
Junhao!

302
00:17:10,520 --> 00:17:11,350
Junhao.

303
00:17:19,280 --> 00:17:20,470
I hope you can think carefully.

304
00:17:22,350 --> 00:17:23,800
Don’t risk Yunyi’s happiness

305
00:17:24,430 --> 00:17:25,950
to cover your scandal.

306
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:28,760
I’ve already thought it through.

307
00:17:29,830 --> 00:17:32,190
There’s no scandal between Qianyu and me.

308
00:17:33,470 --> 00:17:36,000
Neither will I risk Yunyi’s happiness.

309
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:39,640
You’d better keep your promise.

310
00:17:46,040 --> 00:17:46,760
Dawei.

311
00:17:47,310 --> 00:17:48,920
I don’t care what you do

312
00:17:49,230 --> 00:17:50,400
but delete all abusive comments online

313
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:51,800
on Ye Qianyu.

314
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:52,590
Yes.

315
00:17:57,710 --> 00:17:58,520
Boss,

316
00:17:58,760 --> 00:18:01,110
= YUZHU GROUP =
several partners canceled their appointments.

317
00:18:01,640 --> 00:18:04,830
= YUZHU GROUP =
And our commercial is postponed.

318
00:18:05,710 --> 00:18:06,800
What should we do?

319
00:18:13,590 --> 00:18:14,520
Mr. Shan,

320
00:18:14,920 --> 00:18:16,680
you’ve made the headline

321
00:18:16,680 --> 00:18:18,190
several times lately.

322
00:18:19,230 --> 00:18:20,000
Dawei.

323
00:18:20,470 --> 00:18:23,000
Tell Publicity Department
not to issue any statement for now

324
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:24,590
and ask Director Xu

325
00:18:25,230 --> 00:18:27,230
to dig up the source of the news.

326
00:18:27,560 --> 00:18:28,190
Yes.

327
00:18:29,310 --> 00:18:31,520
This matter is no longer about you

328
00:18:31,680 --> 00:18:33,590
but concerns the entire company.

329
00:18:33,950 --> 00:18:35,560
Shouldn’t you give us an explanation?

330
00:18:38,110 --> 00:18:39,160
Mr. Zhang,

331
00:18:39,760 --> 00:18:41,760
if you do care about Senwell,

332
00:18:41,950 --> 00:18:44,430
you’d better spend more time on your work.

333
00:18:44,430 --> 00:18:45,680
I’ve devoted all my time

334
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:47,160
to Senwell,

335
00:18:48,190 --> 00:18:49,350
unlike you

336
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:52,190
who is the center of gossips.

337
00:18:59,310 --> 00:19:00,400
Don’t forget

338
00:19:01,190 --> 00:19:03,000
the board is still waiting for your explanation.

339
00:19:32,070 --> 00:19:33,680
I told you

340
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:35,110
do not drag Ye Qianyu into this

341
00:19:35,110 --> 00:19:36,190
at the moment.

342
00:19:36,560 --> 00:19:38,590
I’m fine with you acting against Shan Junhao,

343
00:19:38,800 --> 00:19:39,800
but I don’t want Senwell

344
00:19:39,800 --> 00:19:41,560
to suffer irreversible losses.

345
00:19:42,070 --> 00:19:42,880
Why didn’t you discuss it with me

346
00:19:42,880 --> 00:19:44,310
before you took action?

347
00:19:45,040 --> 00:19:45,800
Discuss it with you?

348
00:19:46,520 --> 00:19:47,760
Why should I?

349
00:19:49,710 --> 00:19:50,920
You think by doing this,

350
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:52,880
Fan Yunyi will be with you?

351
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:57,110
Do you still remember your goal?

352
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:58,400
Do you want

353
00:19:58,400 --> 00:19:59,950
to get your things back or not?

354
00:20:00,110 --> 00:20:00,880
Get out.

355
00:20:01,950 --> 00:20:03,640
I have no time for you.

356
00:20:08,020 --> 00:20:10,260
= Mr. Qiu =

357
00:20:23,840 --> 00:20:25,210
Gosh!

358
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:29,110
How did this happen?

359
00:20:29,710 --> 00:20:31,520
I don’t know the details

360
00:20:31,520 --> 00:20:33,110
but it seems to be serious.

361
00:20:33,110 --> 00:20:35,070
So I didn’t bring Qianyu back with me.

362
00:20:35,430 --> 00:20:36,190
Jinzhi.

363
00:20:36,560 --> 00:20:38,000
You and Shengzhe

364
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,310
can stay with us these days.

365
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:41,430
If you need anything,

366
00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:42,950
I’ll go to your store to get it.

367
00:20:45,190 --> 00:20:46,950
We didn’t do anything wrong.

368
00:20:47,230 --> 00:20:49,040
Why should we hide ourselves?

369
00:20:49,590 --> 00:20:50,710
Mama Jinzhi.

370
00:20:50,830 --> 00:20:52,350
Cyber-violence is horrible.

371
00:20:52,430 --> 00:20:53,520
You’d better

372
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:55,560
stay away from the media.

373
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:58,700
Shouldn’t Shan Junhao

374
00:20:58,700 --> 00:21:00,360
respond to it?

375
00:21:00,360 --> 00:21:01,870
What could he say?

376
00:21:01,870 --> 00:21:03,870
They did date for a while.

377
00:21:06,110 --> 00:21:07,950
I feel sorry for Qianyu.

378
00:21:07,950 --> 00:21:09,190
What do they know?

379
00:21:09,880 --> 00:21:11,800
No, I’ll

380
00:21:11,800 --> 00:21:13,470
speak for Qianyu in the comments section.

381
00:21:15,190 --> 00:21:16,040
How do you do that?

382
00:21:16,040 --> 00:21:17,000
Teach me.

383
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:18,110
I’ll speak for her, too.

384
00:21:18,110 --> 00:21:19,230
Yes, me too.

385
00:21:23,280 --> 00:21:25,070
Mama Jinzhi, don’t worry too much.

386
00:21:25,190 --> 00:21:26,640
I’ll protect Qianyu.

387
00:21:27,110 --> 00:21:28,000
See?

388
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:31,040
Just calm down and stay here.

389
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:39,680
Taichu.

390
00:21:39,680 --> 00:21:41,040
How are Chen and Shengzhe?

391
00:21:41,800 --> 00:21:44,110
Tang let them stay in the inn.

392
00:21:46,560 --> 00:21:47,680
It’s all my fault

393
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:49,230
that Chen and Shengzhe get implicated.

394
00:21:51,710 --> 00:21:52,830
Don’t blame yourself.

395
00:21:53,040 --> 00:21:54,040
They’re fine

396
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:55,680
but they’re worried about you.

397
00:22:09,520 --> 00:22:10,430
Taichu.

398
00:22:11,310 --> 00:22:12,110
I’ve been thinking

399
00:22:12,110 --> 00:22:13,760
how things turned out like this.

400
00:22:14,470 --> 00:22:16,110
Now, I have the answer.

401
00:22:16,520 --> 00:22:17,310
Shan Junhao and I

402
00:22:17,310 --> 00:22:19,110
belong to different worlds.

403
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:22,160
He can’t cut ties with his world,

404
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:24,190
yet I

405
00:22:24,760 --> 00:22:27,040
keep causing him trouble.

406
00:22:29,310 --> 00:22:31,160
You might be a trouble

407
00:22:32,230 --> 00:22:33,590
in his world.

408
00:22:35,160 --> 00:22:36,430
But to me,

409
00:22:38,230 --> 00:22:39,950
you’re my whole world.

410
00:22:43,880 --> 00:22:44,830
Leave with me.

411
00:22:49,830 --> 00:22:51,560
Leaving means running away.

412
00:22:52,230 --> 00:22:53,590
I don’t want to do that.

413
00:22:54,520 --> 00:22:56,190
No matter how this will end,

414
00:22:56,710 --> 00:22:57,760
I’ll accept it.

415
00:22:58,190 --> 00:22:59,110
Qianyu,

416
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:01,760
leaving doesn’t mean running away

417
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,950
but embracing a new self.

418
00:23:05,000 --> 00:23:07,520
You’ll see different people and things,

419
00:23:07,950 --> 00:23:09,760
then you’ll realize there are many things

420
00:23:09,760 --> 00:23:12,000
that you love and care.

421
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:14,710
If you miss here,

422
00:23:14,710 --> 00:23:16,190
you can come back anytime.

423
00:23:19,520 --> 00:23:20,880
Leaving

424
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:23,000
isn’t about time and space

425
00:23:23,400 --> 00:23:24,830
but moving on with your life.

426
00:23:40,680 --> 00:23:41,800
Before I leave,

427
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:44,140
I have an important thing to do.

428
00:23:49,590 --> 00:23:50,350
OK.

429
00:23:51,930 --> 00:23:53,080
Congratulations

430
00:23:53,210 --> 00:23:54,140
on your early release.

431
00:23:54,470 --> 00:23:57,180
Thanks for your help, Mr. Zhang.

432
00:23:57,440 --> 00:23:59,850
Otherwise, we couldn’t sit here together.

433
00:23:59,850 --> 00:24:00,970
Yes, Mr. Zhang.

434
00:24:01,000 --> 00:24:02,380
- Here. - Thanks for everything you did for us.

435
00:24:02,560 --> 00:24:04,270
We’ll pay you back handsomely.

436
00:24:04,270 --> 00:24:04,880
Yours.

437
00:24:08,950 --> 00:24:09,590
You’re welcome.

438
00:24:10,760 --> 00:24:12,160
Shan Junhao is merciless

439
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:13,560
but I’m not.

440
00:24:18,070 --> 00:24:19,070
Mr. Zhang,

441
00:24:19,070 --> 00:24:21,230
his name alone

442
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:24,190
gets me hot under the collar.

443
00:24:24,350 --> 00:24:26,430
We ended up in jail

444
00:24:26,430 --> 00:24:29,680
because of that little bastard!

445
00:24:31,880 --> 00:24:33,560
Not only that,

446
00:24:33,560 --> 00:24:35,920
he bought our shares at a low price.

447
00:24:36,300 --> 00:24:38,600
Now, he’s in hot water.

448
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:42,030
Actually, I knew

449
00:24:42,030 --> 00:24:43,950
his affair with Ye Qianyu
would be exposed one day,

450
00:24:44,110 --> 00:24:45,400
but I didn’t expect

451
00:24:45,400 --> 00:24:46,590
it’d be so explosive.

452
00:24:49,710 --> 00:24:50,470
Mr. Zhang,

453
00:24:50,560 --> 00:24:51,430
what do you think?

454
00:24:51,430 --> 00:24:53,110
Isn’t our idea great?

455
00:24:53,760 --> 00:24:56,070
Xu Ziqian and Shan Junhao

456
00:24:56,070 --> 00:24:57,590
are officially on opposing sides.

457
00:24:57,830 --> 00:24:58,640
What’s more,

458
00:24:58,880 --> 00:25:02,070
Xu Ziqian has become one of us.

459
00:25:02,310 --> 00:25:04,110
It’s not easy

460
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:06,400
to destroy Shan Junhao.

461
00:25:07,230 --> 00:25:07,880
By the way,

462
00:25:07,950 --> 00:25:09,800
you didn’t ask me out

463
00:25:09,800 --> 00:25:12,560
only to catch up, did you?

464
00:25:13,830 --> 00:25:15,070
You’re smart.

465
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:16,920
Nothing can be concealed from you.

466
00:25:18,760 --> 00:25:19,830
We have

467
00:25:20,640 --> 00:25:23,040
something for you today.

468
00:25:23,830 --> 00:25:25,000
What is it?

469
00:25:25,110 --> 00:25:27,040
It’s marvelous.

470
00:25:27,590 --> 00:25:31,350
It can bury Shan Junhao instantly.

471
00:25:37,800 --> 00:25:40,950
This is a copy of the equity transfer agreement

472
00:25:41,110 --> 00:25:44,760
= Equity Transfer Agreement of Senwell=
between Xu Yifeng and Shan Yaolong.

473
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:47,230
What’s the use of it?

474
00:25:48,070 --> 00:25:48,920
This is

475
00:25:49,190 --> 00:25:52,760
the news report of Changfeng Yacht’s explosion.

476
00:25:52,760 --> 00:25:55,350
Check the dates on the two files.

477
00:25:55,740 --> 00:25:56,540
= Boat Crashed Searching for the Missing =

478
00:25:56,560 --> 00:25:59,350
Right after Xu Yifeng sold his shares,

479
00:25:59,560 --> 00:26:02,190
= Xu Yifeng and His Wife Died in Boat Crash =
his yacht exploded on the same day.

480
00:26:03,470 --> 00:26:04,950
What’s the connection?

481
00:26:08,070 --> 00:26:09,590
Think about it.

482
00:26:09,950 --> 00:26:11,760
Shan Yaolong forced Xu Yifeng

483
00:26:11,760 --> 00:26:14,040
to sign the equity transfer agreement.

484
00:26:14,190 --> 00:26:15,920
On the same day,

485
00:26:16,190 --> 00:26:18,190
Xu Yifeng died in the accident.

486
00:26:18,950 --> 00:26:20,520
And his yacht

487
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:24,880
was a gift from Shan Yaolong.

488
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:27,710
Piece the three incidents altogether.

489
00:26:28,310 --> 00:26:30,000
Isn’t it obvious?

490
00:26:30,760 --> 00:26:33,710
Shan Yaolong gave that yacht to Xu Yifeng?

491
00:26:33,980 --> 00:26:35,040
- Yes. - Correct.

492
00:26:36,470 --> 00:26:38,000
Are you saying

493
00:26:39,680 --> 00:26:42,560
the explosion isn’t an accident

494
00:26:43,160 --> 00:26:45,110
but was planned by Shan Yaolong?

495
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:46,830
Exactly.

496
00:26:47,310 --> 00:26:51,070
Those three incidents seem to be related

497
00:26:51,800 --> 00:26:53,680
but the connection is still thin.

498
00:26:54,230 --> 00:26:54,920
Also,

499
00:26:56,950 --> 00:26:58,160
this time,

500
00:26:58,310 --> 00:27:00,880
we’ve found a key witness

501
00:27:00,880 --> 00:27:02,160
who can prove that

502
00:27:02,160 --> 00:27:04,000
the explosion

503
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:06,110
was Shan Yaolong’s doing.

504
00:27:07,280 --> 00:27:08,280
Have a look.

505
00:27:11,620 --> 00:27:13,380
= Testimony =

506
00:27:17,140 --> 00:27:19,300
= Ding Yuanxun =

507
00:27:20,920 --> 00:27:22,280
Ding Yuanxun?

508
00:27:22,430 --> 00:27:24,190
Yes. Ding Yuanxun.

509
00:27:42,950 --> 00:27:43,590
Yunyi.

510
00:27:44,520 --> 00:27:45,400
Yunyi.

511
00:27:45,920 --> 00:27:47,560
I bought you flowers.

512
00:27:58,760 --> 00:28:00,360
Sunflowers.

513
00:28:01,560 --> 00:28:02,880
You like them?

514
00:28:14,040 --> 00:28:16,000
Without the sun,

515
00:28:17,160 --> 00:28:19,160
sunflowers will die, won’t they?

516
00:28:40,040 --> 00:28:41,710
We’re in pain

517
00:28:43,640 --> 00:28:45,640
most likely because we refuse to let go.

518
00:28:46,830 --> 00:28:49,760
Junhao isn’t someone I can let go

519
00:28:50,070 --> 00:28:52,230
but I can’t live without him.

520
00:28:54,280 --> 00:28:55,110
Yunyi.

521
00:28:56,230 --> 00:28:57,640
All these years,

522
00:28:59,280 --> 00:29:01,230
I’ve chosen to stand behind you,

523
00:29:04,190 --> 00:29:05,190
but I realized

524
00:29:05,880 --> 00:29:06,950
my sacrifice

525
00:29:09,280 --> 00:29:11,640
didn’t lead you to the right choice.

526
00:29:17,830 --> 00:29:19,430
Now, I want you to know

527
00:29:20,590 --> 00:29:22,470
I can be your sun, too.

528
00:29:34,040 --> 00:29:35,190
I’m sorry, Ziqian.

529
00:29:37,560 --> 00:29:38,590
I think

530
00:29:39,280 --> 00:29:41,040
you can understand how I feel

531
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:45,160
because to some extent,

532
00:29:46,710 --> 00:29:49,160
our experiences are similar.

533
00:30:07,520 --> 00:30:08,470
It’s OK.

534
00:30:11,110 --> 00:30:12,920
I’ve spent so much time on you

535
00:30:13,830 --> 00:30:14,760
and I’m willing to

536
00:30:16,560 --> 00:30:17,560
to spend more.

537
00:30:30,020 --> 00:30:32,340
= Zhang Minghan =

538
00:30:34,230 --> 00:30:35,430
If it’s work,

539
00:30:35,920 --> 00:30:37,430
you should go.

540
00:30:40,590 --> 00:30:41,400
No worries.

541
00:30:42,230 --> 00:30:43,640
I want to stay for a few more minutes.

542
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:52,280
- Mr. Shan. - Shan Junhao.

543
00:30:52,280 --> 00:30:53,800
Is your relationship with Ye Qianyu true?

544
00:30:53,800 --> 00:30:54,640
Mr. Shan. Give us an answer.

545
00:30:54,920 --> 00:30:55,520
Excuse me.

546
00:30:55,520 --> 00:30:56,350
Can you explain it?

547
00:30:56,350 --> 00:30:58,280
Excuse me. Make a way.

548
00:30:58,280 --> 00:31:00,190
Mr. Shan.

549
00:31:00,830 --> 00:31:01,580
Have you considered

550
00:31:01,580 --> 00:31:02,510
your fiancée’s feelings?

551
00:31:02,510 --> 00:31:03,600
Mr. Shan, please answer the questions.

552
00:31:03,600 --> 00:31:04,800
Is the latest rumor true?

553
00:31:04,800 --> 00:31:06,410
Isn’t she that village girl?

554
00:31:06,590 --> 00:31:07,260
Ye Qianyu,

555
00:31:07,260 --> 00:31:08,890
don’t you know Shan Junhao is already engaged?

556
00:31:08,890 --> 00:31:09,690
Did Mr. Shan

557
00:31:09,690 --> 00:31:10,830
give you the job in Senwell?

558
00:31:14,950 --> 00:31:15,760
Ye Qianyu,

559
00:31:17,180 --> 00:31:18,040
I said

560
00:31:18,830 --> 00:31:20,090
- I wouldn’t... - I know

561
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:22,880
you wouldn’t have mercy on anyone

562
00:31:23,070 --> 00:31:24,310
who slandered you or Senwell.

563
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:29,430
As the person involved,

564
00:31:30,190 --> 00:31:31,920
I should tell you the truth.

565
00:31:32,920 --> 00:31:34,760
When Shan Junhao lost his memory,

566
00:31:35,110 --> 00:31:37,350
he did stay in Guanmei Fishing Village
for a while.

567
00:31:37,880 --> 00:31:39,280
At that time,

568
00:31:39,560 --> 00:31:41,000
he made friends with me

569
00:31:41,470 --> 00:31:43,710
and everyone else there.

570
00:31:44,190 --> 00:31:45,400
Other than friends,

571
00:31:47,230 --> 00:31:48,680
